videos.headline: Hamilton suffers knee injury
videos.description: UCF running back Jawon Hamilton is carted off the field after what appears to be a knee injury.

videos.headline: UCF stuffs Maryland on 4th and 1
videos.description: UCF's defense stops Maryland on a quarterback sneak attempt.

videos.headline: McGowan scores his 2nd TD of the game
videos.description: Taj McGowan's 3-yard touchdown run is his second score of the game.

videos.headline: Milton breaks off big run
videos.description: McKenzie Milton takes designed quarterback run 55 yards.

videos.headline: Milton hits Akins for TD
videos.description: Jordan Akins grabs a pass from McKenzie Milton in end zone to extend the UCF lead.

videos.headline: Moore grabs Maryland's first TD
videos.description: D.J. Moore takes Max Bortenschlager's pass to the house to score the first touchdown of the game for the Terrapins.

videos.headline: Lowry bull rushes potential blocker
videos.description: Seyvon Lowry dominates blocker leading to a sack for UCF.

videos.headline: Killins Jr. goes untouched on touchdown run
videos.description: Adrian Killins Jr. runs for a 15-yard touchdown to extend the UCF lead.

videos.headline: Hughes takes interception to the house
videos.description: Mike Hughes snags ball that bounced off of receiver's hands and returns it for a touchdown.
